channel.title: Tele commands stopped working
channel.description:
When i was adding some new commands half my tele commands (::boat, ::agility ::smithing etc) stopped working and i can't fix them. I tried replacing what i added with the old stuff from command back up but it didnt work.
how can i fix these, please!!

item.title: Tele commands stopped working
item.dc:creator: @PlucScape PlucScape
item.description:
@PlucScape wrote:

You most likely didn’t place your new commands at the right place in your source…
Maybe you also forgot to close a bracket
For instance if you open 3 you should close them all 3 when you’re done. Example;
Code1 {
code 2{
code 3{
code 5
}
}
}

That avoids having one big chunk of useless writing
